  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male and female patients with limbal stem cell deficiency

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Bilateral limbal stem cell deficiency

          -  Unilateral limbal stem cell deficiency with more than 50% of damage to the
             contralateral eye

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Breast-feeding

          -  Minors

          -  known allergy to aprotinine (Trasylol (R))

          -  Hypersensibility to bovine proteins
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
